									</dimensions>
									<dimensions type="written" unit="mm">
										<height>200</height>
										<width>125</width>
									</dimensions>
								</extent>
								<foliation>
									<p>193 folios  (+ 2 unfoliated paper flyleaves at the beginning and at the end)</p>
									<p>Originally consisted of 210 folios.</p>
								</foliation>
								<collation>
									<p>Originally 21 quires of 10 leaves each, currently incompele at the beginning, with some folios missing throughout.</p>
									<p>The quires were marked with catchwords and also signed with Hebrew letters on the last and first pages respectively.</p>
								</collation>
